Package: sunshine
Type: Package
Title: Calculator for sun position related quantities (e.g. sunrise and sunset times)
Version: 0.1
Date: 2013-01-11
Author: Colin Rundel <rundel@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Colin Rundel <rundel@gmail.com>
Description: Package for calculating various quantities regarding the sun's position e.g. solar angle, sunrise and sunset times, sunlight duration, etc. Calculations are based NOAA's solar calculator (http://www.esrl.noaa.gov/gmd/grad/solcalc/calcdetails.html).
License: LGPL
Depends: lubridate (>= 1.2.0), proj4 (>= 1.0-8), timezone